        <text>
            <body>
                
                    <p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324645" xml:id="d1e132724" corresp="Étienne II, évêque d'Autun (1171-1189)">Stephanus, Dei gratia
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e132726" corresp="Autun (Saône-et-Loire, Autun)">Eduensis</placeName> episcopus</persName>, tam futuris quam
                        presentibus, notum fieri volo quod <persName key="d1e12127" xml:id="d1e132730">Savericus</persName>, <persName key="d1e12133" xml:id="d1e132733">Andreas</persName> et <persName key="d1e12140" xml:id="d1e132736">Herveus</persName>, <lb n="2" /> filii <persName key="d1e12146" xml:id="d1e132742">Odonis de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324452" xml:id="d1e132744" corresp="Fontaines-en-Duesmois (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Fontanis</placeName>
                        </persName>, laudante matre sua <persName key="d1e12152" xml:id="d1e132747">Alwiz</persName> et sororibus suis <persName key="d1e12158" xml:id="d1e132750">Alwiz</persName>, <persName key="d1e12164" xml:id="d1e132753">Tecelina</persName> et <persName key="d1e12170" xml:id="d1e132756">Gertrude</persName>, laudaverunt in presentia <lb n="3" /> mea donum quod pater suus ad conversionem veniens <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e132762" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetensi ecclesie</orgName>
                        fecerat. Donum autem ipsum hujusmodi est : ut <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e132765" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fon<lb n="4" break="no" />tenentenses</orgName>
                        quotiens sibi placuerit per totum finem <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324452" xml:id="d1e132770" corresp="Fontaines-en-Duesmois (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Fontanarum</placeName>, omni tempore, in plano et in
                        bosco et in aquis, absque <lb n="5" /> damno messium et pratorum, pecora sua
                        libere pastum mittant et de boschis ejusdem ville tollant que pecoribus vel
                            pa<lb n="6" break="no" />storibus suis ibidem morantibus necessaria
                        fuerint, ad bordam scilicet, ad focum, ad umbracula et ad ceteros idoneos
                        usus, ita <lb n="7" /> sane ut si pecora <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e132780" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetensium</orgName> in prato vel messe damnum
                        aliquod intulerint absque alia lege damnum solummodo reddent. <lb n="8" />
                        Hoc donum patris sui jampridem laudaverant predicti fratres. Postea vero
                        idem donum tam ipsi quam mater eorum atque sorores <lb n="9" /> prenominate
                        ex parte sua fecerunt <note> Sic « ex parte″ fecerunt ″sua ».</note>,
                        adicientes insuper et donantes prefate ecclesie monachis pastionem ad porcos
                            <lb n="10" /> suos per nemora sua. Concesserunt etiam quod nullos homines
                        alterius religionis in ipsas pasturas vel usuaria <lb n="11" /> mittent, nisi
                        tantum habitatores <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324452" xml:id="d1e132796" corresp="Fontaines-en-Duesmois (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Fontanarum</placeName>, necnon ad opus animalium monachorum per terram
                        suam et per mediam <lb n="12" /> riveriam, unam carreriam trium tesiarum.
                        Dimiserunt quoque prefate ecclesie totam calumniam quam habebant in <lb n="13" /> territorio <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324375" xml:id="d1e132803" corresp="Verdonnet (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Verdennaci</placeName>, nichil inibi retinentes infra metas versus
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324375" xml:id="d1e132806" corresp="Verdonnet (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Verdennacum</placeName>, que communi assensu, ipsorum scilicet et mo<lb n="14" break="no" />nachorum posite sunt, nisi pasturas animalibus
                        hominum suorum et pastionem porcis eorum. Et si damnum <lb n="15" /> fecerint
                        monachis animalia <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324452" xml:id="d1e132814" corresp="Fontaines-en-Duesmois (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Fontanarum</placeName>, sine alia lege damnum restituent. Hec etiam
                        laudaverunt homines <lb n="16" /> ipsius ville qui dicebant se habere usagium
                        in predicto <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324375" xml:id="d1e132819" corresp="Verdonnet (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Verdennaci</placeName> territorio, et omnem calumniam quam ha<lb n="17" break="no" />bebant ibi pro animabus suis ecclesie Fontenetensi
                        guerpierunt, nichil penitus excipientes, nisi quod in orationibus et
                        beneficiis <lb n="18" /> ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e132827" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> recipientur, quorum sunt nomina
                            <persName key="d1e12177" xml:id="d1e132830">Christianus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324960" xml:id="d1e132832" corresp="Monte Canino">Monte Canino</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e12183" xml:id="d1e132835">Hugo</persName> et
                            <persName key="d1e12189" xml:id="d1e132838">Odo</persName>, <persName key="d1e12195" xml:id="d1e132841">Brictius</persName> et <persName key="d1e12201" xml:id="d1e132845">Wido</persName>, <lb n="19" /> filius
                        ejus, <persName key="d1e12207" xml:id="d1e132850">Petrus major filius
                                <persName key="d1e12214" xml:id="d1e132852">Theobaldi de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325259" xml:id="d1e132854" corresp="Cumba">Cumba</placeName>
                            </persName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e12220" xml:id="d1e132857">Henricus</persName>
                        etiam et fratres ejus, <persName key="d1e12226" xml:id="d1e132860">Petrinus</persName> et <persName key="d1e12232" xml:id="d1e132863">Willelmus</persName>, et <persName key="d1e12238" xml:id="d1e132867">Beris</persName> eorum avunculus, <lb n="20" /> et <persName key="d1e12244" xml:id="d1e132872">Hugo <addName>Albus</addName>
                        </persName>. Horum testes sunt <persName key="d1e12251" xml:id="d1e132877">Willelmus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324336" xml:id="d1e132879" corresp="Orgeux (Côte-d'Or, Fontaine-lès-Dijon)">
                                <foreign>Orgeol</foreign>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e12257" xml:id="d1e132883">Audo vicecomes
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324442" xml:id="d1e132885" corresp="Duesme (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Duismi</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e12263" xml:id="d1e132888">Haimo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324402" xml:id="d1e132890" corresp="Aisey-sur-Seine (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">
                                <foreign>Aise</foreign>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e12269" xml:id="d1e132895">Hugo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324912" xml:id="d1e132897" corresp="Aizanville">Asenvilla</placeName>
                        </persName>. <lb n="21" /> Hec ita laudavit <persName key="d1e12275" xml:id="d1e132902">Pontius <addName>
                                <foreign>Chenlarz</foreign>
                            </addName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e12281" xml:id="d1e132908">Willelma</persName> uxor ejus ; unde sunt testes <persName key="d1e12288" xml:id="d1e132911">Lambertus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324432" xml:id="d1e132913" corresp="Conforgien (Côte-d'Or, Arnay-le-Duc)">
                                <foreign>Corfergen</foreign>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e12294" xml:id="d1e132917">Bernardus</persName> frater ejus, <lb n="22" />
                        <persName key="d1e12300" xml:id="d1e132922">Girardus
                                <addName>Pilosus</addName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e12306" xml:id="d1e132927">Guiardus</persName> filius ejus. Hec omnia laudavit <persName key="d1e12312" xml:id="d1e132930">Elisabeth, filia <persName key="d1e12318" xml:id="d1e132932">Saverici</persName>
                        </persName>. Unde sunt testes <lb n="23" />
                        <persName key="d1e12325" xml:id="d1e132936">Letardus presbiter</persName>,
                            <persName key="d1e12331" xml:id="d1e132939">Wido de Frollesio
                            monachus</persName>, <persName key="d1e12337" xml:id="d1e132943">Walterius prepositus</persName>, <persName key="d1e12343" xml:id="d1e132946">Airardus</persName>, <persName key="d1e12349" xml:id="d1e132949">Reinaldus</persName>, <persName key="d1e12355" xml:id="d1e132952">Engirbertus magister <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325154" xml:id="d1e132954" corresp="Carbonerum">Carbonerum</placeName>
                        </persName>. <lb n="24" /> Ego igitur hec omnia sigilli mei munimine signans,
                        ne quis ulterius de his ecclesia <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e132959" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> vexare aut perturbare presumat
                        episcopali anatematizans virtute perhibeo.</p>
                
